8:6 Ab'aho benshi baraterana, bumva ibyo Filipo avuga n'umutima uhuye bamwitayeho, bumvise kandi babonye ibimenyetso yakoraga. 
8:7 Kuko benshi muri bo bari bafite abadayimoni babavamo basakuza cyane, n'abari baremaye n'abacumbagira benshi barakizwa. 
8:8 Haba umunezero mwinshi muri uwo mudugudu.
