8:10 Baramwumvaga bamwitayeho bose, abakomeye n'aboroheje bati “Uyu muntu ni we Mbaraga y'Imana yitwa ikomeye.” 
8:11 Icyatumaga bamwitaho, ni uko uhereye kera yajyaga abatangarisha iby'ubukonikoni bwe. 
8:12 Ariko bamaze kwizera ubutumwa bwiza Filipo ababwira bw'ubwami bw'Imana n'ubw'izina rya Yesu Kristo, barabatizwa, abagabo n'abagore. 
8:13 Na Simoni ubwe aremera, kandi amaze kubatizwa agumya kubana na Filipo. Abonye uburyo akora ibimenyetso n'imirimo ikomeye arumirwa.
8:14 Nuko intumwa zari i Yerusalemu zumvise yuko Abasamariya bemeye ijambo ry'Imana, zibatumaho Petero na Yohana, 
8:15 na bo basohoyeyo barabasabira ngo bahabwe Umwuka Wera, 
8:16 kuko hari hataragira n'umwe wo muri bo amanukira, ahubwo bari barabatijwe gusa mu izina ry'Umwami Yesu. 
8:17 Nuko babarambikaho ibiganza, bahabwa Umwuka Wera.
