8:22 Nuko wihane ubwo bubi bwawe, usabe Umwami kugira ngo ahari niba bishoboka, ibyo wibwira mu mutima wawe ubibabarirwe. 
8:23 Ndakureba uri mu birura no mu ngoyi zo gukiranirwa.”
8:24 Simoni aramusubiza ati “Munsabire Umwami, kugira ngo hatagira ikintu kimbaho mu byo muvuze.”
8:25 Na bo bamaze guhamya no kubwira abantu ijambo ry'Umwami, basubira i Yerusalemu babwiriza ubutumwa bwiza mu birorero byinshi by'Abasamariya.
