9:1 Ariko Sawuli akomeza gukangisha abigishwa b'Umwami ko bicwa, ajya ku mutambyi mukuru 
9:2 amusaba inzandiko zo guha ab'amasinagogi y'i Damasiko, kugira ngo nabona abantu b'Inzira ya Yesu, abagabo cyangwa abagore, ababohe abajyane i Yerusalemu.
9:3 Akigenda yenda gusohora i Damasiko, umucyo uramutungura uvuye mu ijuru uramugota. 
9:4 Agwa hasi yumva ijwi rimubaza riti “Sawuli, Sawuli, undenganiriza iki?”
9:5 Aramubaza ati “Uri nde, Mwami?”
9:6 Ariko haguruka ujye mu mudugudu, uzabwirwa ibyo ukwiriye gukora.”
9:7 Abagabo bajyanye na we bahagarara badakoma, kuko bumvise iryo jwi batagize umuntu babona. 
9:8 Sawuli arabyuka arambuye amaso ntiyagira icyo areba, baramurandata bamujyana i Damasiko. 
9:9 Amarayo gatatu atareba, atarya kandi atanywa.
9:10 I Damasiko hari umwigishwa witwaga Ananiya. Umwami Yesu aramubonekera aramuhamagara ati “Ananiya.”
9:11 Umwami aramubwira ati “Haguruka ujye mu nzira yitwa Igororotse, ushakire mu nzu ya Yuda umuntu witwa Sawuli w'i Taruso, kuko ubu ngubu asenga. 
9:12 Kandi na we abonye mu iyerekwa umuntu witwa Ananiya yinjira, amurambikaho ibiganza kugira ngo ahumuke.”
9:13 Ananiya aramusubiza ati “Mwami, uwo muntu numvise benshi bamuvuga, uko yagiriraga nabi abera bawe bari i Yerusalemu, 
9:14 kandi n'ino afite ubutware abuhawe n'abatambyi bakuru, bwo kuboha abāmbaza izina ryawe.”
9:15 Umwami aramusubiza ati “Genda kuko uwo muntu ari igikoreshwa nitoranirije, ngo yogeze izina ryanjye imbere y'abanyamahanga n'abami n'Abisirayeli, 
9:16 nanjye nzamwereka ibyo azababazwa na we uburyo ari byinshi, bamuhora izina ryanjye.”
9:17 Ananiya aragenda yinjira mu nzu, amurambikaho ibiganza aramubwira ati “Sawuli mwene Data, Umwami Yesu wakubonekereye mu nzira waturutsemo, arantumye ngo uhumuke wuzuzwe Umwuka Wera.” 
9:18 Uwo mwanya ibisa n'imboneranyi bimuva ku maso arahumuka, arahaguruka arabatizwa, 
9:19 amaze gufungura abona intege.
9:20 aherako abwiriza mu masinagogi yuko Yesu ari Umwana w'Imana.
9:21 Abamwumvise bose barumirwa bati “Uyu si we warimburiraga i Yerusalemu abāmbaza iryo zina? Kandi icyamuzanye n'ino si ukugira ngo ababohe, abashyīre abatambyi bakuru?”
9:22 Ariko Sawuli arushaho kugwiza imbaraga, atsinda Abayuda batuye i Damasiko arabamwaza, abahamiriza yuko Yesu ari we Kristo.
9:23   </span><span class="note x"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body">    2 Kor 11.32-33  
9:24 ariko Sawuli amenya inama yabo. Bubikirira ku marembo ku manywa na nijoro, kugira ngo bamwice. 
9:25 Abigishwa be ni ko kumujyana nijoro, bamucisha mu nkike z'amabuye, bamumanurira mu gitebo.
9:26 Asohoye i Yerusalemu agerageza kwifatanya n'abigishwa, ariko bose baramutinya ntibemera ko ari umwigishwa. 
9:27 Maze Barinaba aramujyana amushyīra intumwa, azisobanurira uko yabonye Umwami Yesu mu nzira, kandi uko yavuganye na we, n'uko yavuze ashize amanga mu izina rya Yesu i Damasiko. 
9:28 Abana na bo i Yerusalemu akajya abasura, abwiriza mu izina ry'Umwami ashize amanga, 
9:29 akaganira n'Abayuda ba kigiriki ajya impaka na bo, bigeza ubwo na bo bashaka kumwica. 
9:30 Ariko bene Data babimenye bamujyana i Kayisariya, bamwohereza i Taruso.
9:31 Nuko Itorero ryose ryari i Yudaya hose n'i Galilaya n'i Samariya rigira amahoro, rirakomezwa kandi rigenda ryubaha Umwami Yesu, rifashwa n'Umwuka Wera riragwira.
9:32 Nuko Petero ajya hose kubasūra, ajya no ku bera batuye i Luda, 
9:33 asangayo umugabo witwaga Ayineya wamaze imyaka munani atava ku buriri, kuko yari aremaye. 
9:34 Petero aramubwira ati “Ayineya, Yesu Kristo aragukijije, haguruka wisasire.” Uwo mwanya arahaguruka. 
9:35 Abatuye i Luda n'i Saroni bose bamubonye bahindukirira Umwami Yesu.
9:36 Kandi i Yopa hari umugore w'umwigishwa witwaga Tabita, risobanurwa ngo “Doruka”. Uwo mugore yagiraga imirimo myiza myinshi n'ubuntu bwinshi. 
9:37 Muri iyo minsi ararwara arapfa, bamaze kumwuhagira bamushyira mu cyumba cyo hejuru. 
9:38 Kandi kuko i Luda hari bugufi bw'i Yopa, abigishwa bumvise ko Petero ari yo ari, bamutumaho abantu babiri bamwinginga bati “Ngwino uze iwacu, ntutinde.” 
9:39 Petero arahaguruka, ajyana na bo. Asohoyeyo bamujyana muri icyo cyumba cyo hejuru, abapfakazi bose bahagarara iruhande rwe barira, berekana amakanzu n'imyenda Doruka yababoheye akiriho. 
9:40 Petero abaheza bose, arapfukama arasenga, ahindukirira intumbi ati “Tabita, haguruka.” Arambura amaso, abonye Petero arabyuka aricara. 
9:41 Petero amufata ukuboko aramuhagurutsa. Maze ahamagara abera n'abapfakazi, amubaha ari muzima. 
9:42 Bimenyekana i Yopa hose, benshi bizera Umwami. 
9:43 Nuko amara iminsi myinshi i Yopa, acumbitse kwa Simoni w'umuhazi.
10:1 Hariho umuntu w'i Kayisariya witwaga Koruneliyo, umutware utwara umutwe w'abasirikare wo mu ngabo zitwa Italiyana. 
10:2 Yari umuntu w'umunyadini wubahana Imana n'abo mu rugo rwe bose, wagiriraga abantu ubuntu bwinshi, agasenga Imana ubudasiba. 
10:3 Abona ku mugaragaro mu iyerekwa marayika w'Imana yinjiye iwe nko mu isaha ya cyenda y'umunsi, aramuhamagara ati “Koruneliyo.”
10:4 Aramutumbira, aramutinya, aramubaza ati “Ni iki Mwami?”
10:5 Kandi none tuma abantu i Yopa, utumire umuntu witwa Simoni wahimbwe Petero. 
10:6 Acumbitse kwa Simoni w'umuhazi, urugo rwe ruri iruhande rw'inyanja.” 
10:7 Marayika wavuganaga na we amaze kugenda, ahamagara abagaragu be babiri, n'umusirikare w'umunyadini wo mu bamukorera iteka, 
10:8 amaze kubabwira ibyo byose, abatuma i Yopa.
10:9 Bukeye bw'aho bakiri mu nzira benda gusohora mu mudugudu, Petero ajya hejuru y'inzu gusenga nko mu isaha ya gatandatu. 
10:10 Arasonza ashaka kurya, bakibyitegura aba nk'urota 
10:11 abona ijuru rikingutse, maze ikintu kiramanuka gisa n'umwenda w'umukomahasi, gifashwe ku binyita bine kijya hasi. 
10:12 Harimo inyamaswa z'amoko yose zigenza amaguru ane, n'ibikururuka hasi byose, n'ibiguruka mu kirere byose. 
10:13 Ijwi riramubwira riti “Haguruka Petero, ubage urye.”
10:14 Petero ati “Oya Mwami, kuko ntigeze kurya ikizira cyangwa igihumanya.”
