14:26 Batsukira aho barambuka bafata mu Antiyokiya, aho bari bararagirijwe ubuntu bw'Imana ku bw'umurimo barangije.
14:27 Bagezeyo bateranya Itorero, babatekerereza ibyo Imana yakoranye na bo byose, n'uko yugururiye abanyamahanga irembo ryo kwizera. 
14:28 Bamarayo iminsi myinshi bari hamwe n'abigishwa.
15:1   </span><span class="note x"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body">    Lewi 12.3  
15:2 Habaho impaka nyinshi n'imburanya kuri Pawulo na Barinaba n'abo bantu, maze bene Data bahuza inama yo gutuma Pawulo na Barinaba n'abandi muri bo, kujya i Yerusalemu ku ntumwa n'abakuru kugira ngo bajye inama y'izo mpaka.
15:3 Abo bamaze guherekezwa n'Itorero banyura i Foyinike n'i Samariya, basobanurira bene Data uburyo abanyamahanga bahindukiriye Imana. Ibyo bituma bose banezerwa umunezero mwinshi. 
15:4 Basohoye i Yerusalemu, ab'Itorero n'intumwa n'abakuru barabākīra. Nuko na bo babatekerereza ibyo Imana yakoranye na bo byose. 
15:5 Ariko bamwe bo mu gice cy'Abafarisayo bizeye barahaguruka, bavuga yuko abanyamahanga bakwiriye gukebwa no gutegekwa kwitondera amategeko ya Mose.
15:6 Intumwa n'abakuru bateranira kujya inama y'ayo magambo. 
15:7  Habaho imburanya nyinshi, maze Petero arahaguruka, arababwira ati “Bagabo bene Data, muzi yuko kera Imana yantoranyije muri mwe, kugira ngo akanwa kanjye abe ari ko abanyamahanga bumvamo ijambo ry'ubutumwa bwiza bizere. 
15:8  Imana irondōra imitima y'abantu yarabahamije, ubwo yabahaye Umwuka Wera nk'uko yamuduhaye natwe. 
15:9 Ntiyashyiraho itandukaniro ryacu na bo, ahubwo yogesheje imitima yabo kwizera. 
15:10 Nuko ni iki gitumye mugerageza Imana, mwikoreza abigishwa imitwaro ba sogokuruza batashoboye kwikorera, ndetse natwe ni uko? 
15:11 Ahubwo twizera yuko ubuntu bw'Umwami Yesu ari bwo buzadukiza, nk'uko na bo bazakizwa na bwo.”
15:12 Abahateraniye bose barahora, bumva uko Barinaba na Pawulo babatekerereza ibimenyetso n'ibitangaza byose Imana yabahaye gukora mu banyamahanga. 
15:13 Barangije kuvuga Yakobo aravuga ati “Bagabo bene Data, munyumve. 
15:14 Simoni yabatekerereje uko Imana yatangiye kugenderera abanyamahanga, kubatoranyamo ubwoko bwo kūbaha izina ryayo. 
15:15 Amagambo y'abahanuzi ahura n'ibyo nk'uko byanditswe ngo
15:16   </span><span class="note x"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body">    Amosi 9.11-12  
15:17 Kugira ngo abantu basigaye bashakane Uwiteka,
15:18 Ni ko Uwiteka avuga, ari we ukora ibyo byose,
15:19 “Ni cyo gitumye ku bwanjye ntegeka ko tureka kurushya abo mu banyamahanga bahindukirira Imana, 
15:20  ahubwo tubandikire ngo bareke ibihumanya by'ibishushanyo bisengwa, no gusambana, n'ibinizwe, n'amaraso, 
15:21 kuko uhereye kera kose Mose afite mu midugudu yose ababwiriza ibye, bisomerwa mu masinagogi ku masabato yose.”
15:22 Maze intumwa n'abakuru hamwe n'ab'Itorero bose bashima gutoranya abagabo muri bo: ni Yuda witwaga Barisaba na Sila, abantu bakomeye muri bene Data ngo babatumane na Pawulo na Barinaba muri Antiyokiya. 
15:23 Bandika urwandiko bararubaha, rwanditsemo ngo
15:24 Kuko twumvise yuko abantu bavuye muri twe bababwiye amagambo yo guhagarika imitima yanyu, no kuyitera gushidikanya kandi tutabibategetse, 
15:25 twashimye guhuza inama yo gutoranya aba bagabo no kubabatumanaho, n'abo dukunda Barinaba na Pawulo, 
15:26 abantu bahaze amagara yabo ku bw'izina ry'Umwami wacu Yesu Kristo. 
15:27 Nuko dutumye Yuda na Sila, na bo ubwabo bazababwira n'ururimi bimwe n'ibi. 
15:28 Umwuka Wera hamwe natwe, twashimye kutabīkoreza undi mutwaro wose keretse ibi bikwiriye: 
15:29 kwirinda inyama zaterekerejwe ibishushanyo bisengwa, n'amaraso, n'ibinizwe, no gusambana. Ibyo nimubyirinda muzaba mukoze neza. Nuko murabeho.”
15:30 Nuko bamaze gusezererwa baramanuka bajya muri Antiyokiya, bateranya Itorero babaha urwandiko. 
15:31 Barusomye bishimira uko guhugurwa. 
15:32 Yuda na Sila kuko na bo bari abahanuzi, bahugūza bene Data amagambo menshi barabakomeza. 
15:33 Bamaze iminsi bene Data babasezerera amahoro, ngo basubire ku babatumye. [ 
15:34 Ariko Sila we ashima gusigarayo.] 
15:35 Pawulo na Barinaba na bo baguma muri Antiyokiya, bigisha abantu bababwira ijambo ry'Umwami Yesu, bafatanyije n'abandi benshi.
15:36 Hashize iminsi Pawulo abwira Barinaba ati “Dusubire tugenderere bene Data bo mu midugudu yose, aho twavuze ijambo ry'Umwami Yesu tumenye uko bameze.” 
15:37 Barinaba ashaka kujyana na Yohana witwaga Mariko, 
15:38  ariko Pawulo ntiyashima kumujyana, kuko yabahanye i Pamfiliya ntajyane na bo mu murimo. 
15:39 Nuko bagira intonganya nyinshi bituma batandukana, Barinaba ajyana Mariko atsukiraho, arambuka afata i Kupuro. 
15:40 Pawulo na we atoranya Sila, avayo bene Data bamaze kumuragiza ubuntu bw'Umwami Yesu. 
15:41 Anyura i Siriya n'i Kilikiya, akomeza amatorero.
16:1 Nuko agera i Derube n'i Lusitira. Hariyo umwigishwa witwaga Timoteyo umwana w'Umuyudakazi wizeye, ariko se yari Umugiriki. 
16:2 Yashimwaga na bene Data b'i Lusitira n'abo muri Ikoniyo, 
16:3 uwo Pawulo ashaka ko bajyana. Nuko aramujyana aramukeba ku bw'Abayuda bari bahari, kuko bose bari bazi yuko se ari Umugiriki. 
16:4 Bakinyura mu mudugudu, bagenda babwira ab'aho ibyo intumwa n'abakuru b'i Yerusalemu bategetse ngo babyitondere. 
16:5 Nuko amatorero akomerera mu byo kwizera, umubare wabo ukomeza kugwira iminsi yose.
16:6 Bukeye banyura mu gihugu cy'i Furugiya n'i Galatiya, babuzwa n'Umwuka Wera kuvuga ijambo ry'Imana muri Asiya. 
16:7 Bageze ahabangikanye n'i Musiya, bagerageza kujya i Bituniya, ariko Umwuka wa Yesu ntiyabakundira. 
16:8 Nuko banyura i Musiya bagera i Tirowa. 
16:9 Nijoro Pawulo ararota, abona umugabo w'Umunyamakedoniya ahagaze amwinginga ati “Ambuka uze i Makedoniya udutabare.” 
16:10 Amaze kurota izo nzozi, uwo mwanya dushaka kujya i Makedoniya, kuko tumenye yuko Imana iduhamagariye kubabwira ubutumwa bwiza.
16:11 Nuko dutsukira i Tirowa, turaromboreza tujya i Samotirake, bukeye bwaho tugera i Neyapoli, 
16:12 tuvayo tugera i Filipi, ni umudugudu wa mbere wo mu ntara y'i Makedoniya wubatswe n'Abaroma bahimukiye. Tumara iminsi muri uwo mudugudu. 
16:13 Ku munsi w'isabato tuva mu mudugudu tujya ku mugezi inyuma y'irembo, dukeka yuko hariho ahantu ho gusengera. Turicara tuvugana n'abagore bahateraniye. 
16:14 Umugore witwa Ludiya waguraga imyenda y'imihengeri, wo mu mudugudu witwa i Tuwatira, wubahaga Imana aratwumva. Umwami Yesu amwugururira umutima, kugira ngo yite ku byo Pawulo yavugaga. 
16:15 Amaze kubatizanywa n'abo mu rugo rwe, aratwinginga ati “Nimuba mubonye ko nizeye Umwami Yesu by'ukuri, nimuze iwanjye mucumbikeyo.” Araduhata.
16:16 Bukeye tujya aho basengera, duhura n'umuja uragura utewe na dayimoni, yungukiraga ba shebuja cyane n'ingemu. 
16:17 Uwo akurikira Pawulo natwe arasakuza ati “Aba bantu ni abagaragu b'Imana Isumbabyose, kandi barababwira inzira y'agakiza.” 
16:18 Iminsi myinshi agumya kubigenza atyo. Ariko Pawulo abonye ko amurembeje, arahindukira abwira dayimoni ati “Ndagutegetse mu izina rya Yesu Kristo, muvemo!” Amuvamo muri ako kanya.
16:19 Ba shebuja babonye yuko nta ndamu bakimutezeho, bafata Pawulo na Sila barabakurubana babajyana no mu iguriro ku batware, 
16:20 babashyira abacamanza bati “Aba Bayuda bahagarika imitima cyane y'abo mu mudugudu wacu, 
16:21 kandi bigisha imigenzo tuzira kwemera cyangwa kuyikora kuko turi Abaroma.”
16:22 Abari bahateraniye babahagurukirira icyarimwe, abacamanza babatanyaguriza imyenda, bategeka ko babakubita inkoni. 
16:23 Bamaze kubakubita inkoni nyinshi babashyira mu nzu y'imbohe, bategeka umurinzi kubarinda cyane. 
16:24 Na we ategetswe atyo, abajugunya mu nzu yo hagati, akomeza amaguru yabo mu mbago. 
16:25 Ariko mu gicuku Pawulo na Sila barasenga baririmbira Imana, izindi mbohe zirabumva. 
16:26 Uwo mwanya habaho igishyitsi cyinshi, imfatiro z'inzu ziranyeganyega, inzugi zose ziherako zirakinguka, iminyururu ya bose iradohoka. 
16:27 Uwo murinzi arakanguka, abonye inzugi z'inzu y'imbohe zikingutse agira ngo imbohe zacitse, akura inkota ye. 
16:28 Nuko agiye kwiyahura Pawulo avuga ijwi rirenga ati “Wikwigirira nabi twese turi hano.”
16:29 Atumira itabaza, aturumbukira mu nzu ahinda umushyitsi, yikubita imbere ya Pawulo na Sila, 
16:30 maze arabasohokana arababaza ati “Batware nkwiriye gukora nte ngo nkire?”
16:31 Baramusubiza bati “Izere Umwami Yesu, urakira ubwawe n'abo mu rugo rwawe.” 
16:32 Bamubwira ijambo ry'Umwami Yesu n'abo mu rugo rwe bose. 
16:33 Mu gicuku cy'iryo joro arabajyana abuhagira inguma, aherako abatizanywa n'abe bose. 
16:34 Arabazamura abajyana iwe arabagaburira, yishimana cyane n'abo mu rugo rwe bose kuko yizeye Imana.
16:35 Ijoro rikeye ba bacamanza batuma abasirikare babo bati “Rekura abo bantu.”
16:36 Umurinzi w'inzu y'imbohe abwira Pawulo ayo magambo ati “Abacamanza baratumye ngo murekurwe. Nuko rero nimusohoke mugende amahoro.”
16:37 Ariko Pawulo arabasubiza ati “Badukubitiye imbere y'abantu nta rubanza rwadutsinze kandi turi Abaroma, badushyira mu nzu y'imbohe. None barashaka kudukuramo rwihishwa? Reka da! Ahubwo abe ari bo baza ubwabo badusohore.”
16:38 Ayo magambo abasirikare bayabwira abacamanza. Bumvise yuko ari Abaroma baratinya, 
16:39 baraza babasaba imbabazi, barabasohora babasaba kuva muri uwo mudugudu. 
16:40 Bamaze gusohoka mu nzu y'imbohe binjira mwa Ludiya, babona bene Data barabahugura, baragenda.
17:1 Banyura muri Amfipoli no muri Apoloniya bagera i Tesalonike, hariho isinagogi y'Abayuda. 
17:2 Nuko Pawulo nk'uko yamenyereye yinjira muri bo, ajya impaka na bo mu byanditswe ku masabato atatu, 
17:3 abibasobanurira abamenyesha yuko Kristo akwiriye kubabazwa no kuzuka mu bapfuye, kandi ati “Yesu uwo mbabwira ni we Kristo.” 
17:4 Bamwe muri bo barabyemera bifatanya na Pawulo na Sila, n'Abagiriki bubaha Imana benshi na bo ni uko, n'abagore b'icyubahiro batari bake.
17:5 Ariko Abayuda bagira ishyari, bajyana abagabo babi b'inzererezi ziba mu maguriro bateranya igitero, batera imidugararo mu mudugudu, batera inzu ya Yasoni bashaka gukuramo Pawulo na Sila, ngo babashyire imbere y'abantu. 
17:6 Bababuze bakurubana Yasoni na bene Data bamwe, babajyana imbere y'abatwara umudugudu, barasakuza bati “Abubitse ibihugu byose baje n'ino, 
17:7 Yasoni arabacumbikira. Aba bose bagomeye amategeko ya Kayisari, bavuga ko hariho undi Mwami witwa Yesu.” 
17:8 Abatwara umudugudu na rubanda bumvise ibyo, bahagarika imitima. 
17:9 Nuko baka Yasoni n'abandi ingwate, barabarekura.
17:10 Uwo mwanya muri iryo joro bene Data bohereza Pawulo na Sila i Beroya. Basohoyeyo binjira mu isinagogi y'Abayuda. 
17:11 Ariko abo bo bari beza kuruta ab'i Tesalonike, kuko bakīranye ijambo ry'Imana umutima ukunze, bashaka mu byanditswe iminsi yose kugira ngo bamenye yuko ibyo bababwiye ari iby'ukuri koko. 
17:12 Nuko benshi muri bo barizera, n'abagore b'icyubahiro b'Abagiriki, n'abagabo batari bake. 
17:13 Ariko Abayuda b'i Tesalonike bamenye yuko ijambo ry'Imana rivugwa na Pawulo i Beroya, na ho bajyayo boshya rubanda, barababangisha. 
17:14 Uwo mwanya bene Data bohereza Pawulo ngo aveyo ajye ku nyanja, ariko Sila na Timoteyo basigarayo. 
17:15 Nuko abaherekeje Pawulo bamujyana mu Atenayi. Amaze kubategeka kubwira Sila na Timoteyo ngo bamukurikire vuba cyane, basubirayo.
17:16 Ariko Pawulo akibarindiriye muri Atenayi ahagarika umutima cyane, kuko abonye uwo mudugudu wuzuye ibishushanyo bisengwa. 
17:17 Nuko agira impaka mu isinagogi y'Abayuda n'abubaha Imana, kandi no mu iguriro iminsi yose ajya impaka n'abamusangaga. 
17:18 Bamwe mu banyabwenge bitwa Abepikureyo, n'abandi bitwa Abasitoyiko bahura na we. Bamwe muri bo barabazanya bati “Uyu munyamagambo arashaka kuvuga iki?”
17:19 Baramufata bamujyana muri Areyopago baramubaza bati “Mbese twashobora kumenya izo nyigisho nshya uvuga izo ari zo? 
17:20 Ko uzanye amagambo y'inzaduka mu matwi yacu! Nuko rero turashaka kuyamenya ayo ari yo.” 
17:21 Kuko Abanyatenayi bose n'abasuhuke baho batagiraga icyo bakora, keretse gushyushya inkuru no kumva ibyadutse.
17:22 Nuko Pawulo ahagarara hagati ya Areyopago aravuga ati “Bagabo b'Abanyatenayi, mbonye muri byose ko mukabije kwibanda mu by'idini. 
17:23 Ubwo nagendagendaga nitegereza ibyo musenga, nasanze igicaniro cyanditsweho ngo ‘ICY'IMANA ITAMENYWA.’ Nuko iyo musenga mutayizi ni yo mbabwira. 
17:24  Imana yaremye isi n'ibiyirimo byose, Iyo kuko ari yo Mwami w'ijuru n'isi, ntiba mu nsengero zubatswe n'abantu, 
17:25 kandi ntikorerwa n'amaboko y'abantu nk'ugira icyo akennye, kuko ari yo yahaye bose ubugingo no guhumeka n'ibindi byose. 
17:26 Kandi yaremye amahanga yose y'abantu bakomoka ku muntu umwe, ibakwiza mu isi yose. Ni na yo yashyizeho ibihe by'imyaka ko bikuranwa uko yategetse, igabaniriza abantu ingabano z'aho batuye, 
17:27 kugira ngo bashake Imana ngo ahari babashe kuyibona bakabakabye, kandi koko ntiri kure y'umuntu wese muri twe, 
17:28 kuko ari muri yo dufite ubugingo bwacu, tugenda turiho, nk'uko bamwe bo mu bahimbyi b'indirimbo banyu bavuze bati ‘Turi urubyaro rwayo.’
17:29 “Nuko rero ubwo turi urubyaro rw'Imana, ntidukwiriye kwibwira yuko Imana isa n'izahabu cyangwa ifeza cyangwa ibuye, cyangwa ikindi kibajijwe n'ubukorikori bw'abantu n'ubwenge bwabo. 
17:30 Nuko iyo minsi yo kujijwa Imana yarayirengagije, ariko noneho itegeka abantu bose bari hose kwihana, 
17:31 kuko yashyizeho umunsi wo gucira ho urubanza rw'ukuri rw'abari mu isi bose, izarucisha umuntu yatoranije kandi ibyo yabihamirije abantu bose ubwo yamuzuye.”
17:32 Bumvise ibyo kuzuka bamwe barabinegura, abandi bati “Uzabitubwira ubundi.” 
17:33 Nuko Pawulo ava muri bo. 
17:34 Ariko abagabo bamwe bifatanya na we barizera. Harimo Diyonisiyo wo mu ba Areyopago, kandi n'umugore witwaga Damari n'abandi hamwe na bo.
18:1 Hanyuma y'ibyo, Pawulo ava muri Atenayi ajya i Korinto. 
18:2 Asangayo Umuyuda witwaga Akwila wavukiye i Ponto, wari uvanye muri Italiya vuba n'umugore we Purisikila, kuko Kilawudiyo yari yarategetse Abayuda bose kuva i Roma. Nuko ajya kubasūra. 
18:3 Kandi kuko basangira umwuga, abana na bo bakorana imirimo, kuko umwuga wabo wari uwo kuboha amahema. 
18:4 Agira impaka mu isinagogi amasabato yose, yemeza Abayuda n'Abagiriki.
18:5 Maze Sila na Timoteyo baje bavuye i Makedoniya, Pawulo ahatwa n'ijambo ry'Imana, ahamiriza Abayuda yuko Yesu ari we Kristo. 
18:6 Na bo bamugisha impaka batuka Yesu, akunkumura imyenda ye arababwira ati “Amaraso yanyu ababeho, jyeweho ntandiho. Uhereye none ngiye ku banyamahanga.” 
18:7 Aherako avayo, yinjira mu nzu y'umuntu witwaga Titiyo Yusito wubahaga Imana, inzu ye yari ihereranye n'isinagogi. 
18:8 Ariko Kirisipo, umutware w'isinagogi, yizerana Umwami Yesu n'abo mu rugo rwe bose, n'Abakorinto benshi bumvise Pawulo na bo barizera barabatizwa.
18:9 Maze Umwami Yesu abonekera Pawulo nijoro mu nzozi, aramubwira ati “Ntutinye, ahubwo uvuge we guceceka 
18:10 kuko ndi kumwe nawe, kandi nta muntu uzagutera kukugirira nabi, kuko mfite abantu benshi muri uyu mudugudu.” 
18:11 Amarayo umwaka n'amezi atandatu, yigisha ijambo ry'Imana muri bo.
18:12 Ariko ubwo Galiyo yari umutware wo muri Akaya, Abayuda bahuza inama. Nuko batera Pawulo bamujyana imbere y'intebe y'imanza bati 
18:13 “Uyu yemeza abantu gusenga Imana mu buryo budahura n'amategeko.”
18:14 Pawulo yenda guterura amagambo, Galiyo abwira Abayuda ati “Mwa Bayuda mwe, iyo haba hariho igicumuro cyangwa icyaha kibi, haba habonetse impamvu ko mbihanganira kubumva, 
18:15 ariko ubwo hariho impaka z'amagambo n'iz'amazina n'iz'amategeko yanyu, nimubyirangirize, sinshaka guca urubanza rw'ibyo, ni ibyanyu.” 
18:16 Abirukana imbere y'intebe y'imanza. 
18:17 Abagiriki bose bafata Sositeni umutware w'isinagogi, bamukubitira imbere y'intebe y'imanza. Ariko Galiyo ntiyabyitaho.
18:18   </span><span class="note x"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body">    Kub 6.18  
18:19 Bagera muri Efeso ba bandi abasigayo. Nuko yinjira mu isinagogi ajya impaka n'Abayuda. 
18:20 Bamwingingira gutindayo iyindi minsi, ariko ntiyabakundira. 
18:21 Ahubwo abasezeraho arababwira ati “Nzagaruka ubundi, Imana nibishaka.” Atsukira aho ava muri Efeso.
18:22 Arambuka afata i Kayisariya, arazamuka ajya i Yerusalemu aramutsa ab'Itorero, aramanuka ajya muri Antiyokiya. 
18:23 Amarayo iminsi, bukeye aragenda anyura mu gihugu cy'i Galatiya n'i Furugiya, ajya mu midugudu uko ikurikirana, akomeza abigishwa bose.
18:24 Hariho Umuyuda witwaga Apolo wavukiye mu Alekizanderiya, bukeye agera muri Efeso. Yari umuntu w'intyoza w'umunyabwenge, kandi akaba n'umuhanga mu byanditswe. 
18:25 Uwo yari yarigishijwe Inzira y'Umwami Yesu, yagiraga umwete mwinshi mu mutima, avuga ibya Yesu kandi abyigisha neza, ariko yari azi umubatizo wa Yohana gusa. 
18:26 Atangira kuvugira mu masinagogi ashize amanga, maze Purisikila na Akwila bamwumvise bamujyana iwabo, bamusobanurira Inzira y'Imana kugira ngo arusheho kuyimenya neza. 
18:27 Ashatse kwambuka ngo ajye muri Akaya bene Data baramukomeza, bandikira abigishwa ngo bamwakire. Na we asohoyeyo, ubuntu bw'Imana bumutera gufasha cyane abizeye, 
18:28 kuko yatsindiraga Abayuda cyane imbere y'abantu, abereka mu byanditswe yuko Yesu ari we Kristo.
19:1 Apolo ari i Korinto, Pawulo anyura mu bihugu byo haruguru asohora muri Efeso, asangayo abigishwa bamwe. 
19:2 Arababaza ati “Mwahawe Umwuka Wera, mutangiye kwizera?”
19:3 Arababaza ati “Mwabatijwe mubatizo ki?”
19:4   </span><span class="note x"><span class="label">#</span><span class=" body">    Mat 3.11; Mar 1.4; 7-8; Luka 3.4,16; Yoh 1.26-27  
19:5 Babyumvise batyo babatizwa mu izina ry'Umwami Yesu. 
19:6 Pawulo amaze kubarambikaho ibiganza Umwuka Wera abazaho, bavuga izindi ndimi barahanura. 
19:7 Abo bantu bose bari nka cumi na babiri.
19:8 Yinjira mu isinagogi, amara amezi atatu avuga ashize amanga, ajya impaka na bo abemeza iby'ubwami bw'Imana. 
19:9 Ariko bamwe binangiye imitima banga kwizera, batukira Inzira ya Yesu imbere y'abantu. Ava muri bo arobanura abigishwa, iminsi yose agīra impaka mu nzu yo kwigishirizamo ya Turano. 
19:10 Agumya kugira atyo amara imyaka ibiri. Nuko abatuye muri Asiya bose bumva ijambo ry'Umwami Yesu, Abayuda n'Abagiriki.
19:11 Kandi Imana yakoreshaga amaboko ya Pawulo ibitangaza bikomeye. 
19:12 Ndetse bashyīraga abarwayi ibitambaro n'imyenda bivuye ku mubiri we bagakira indwara zabo, abadayimoni bakabavamo. 
19:13 Ariko inzererezi zimwe zo mu Bayuda na zo zirukanaga abadayimoni, zīhimbira kuvugira izina ry'Umwami Yesu ku batewe n'abadayimoni ziti “Ndabategetse mu izina rya Yesu, uwo Pawulo avuga.” 
19:14 Kandi hariho abahungu barindwi b'Umuyuda witwaga Sikewa, umwe mu batambyi bakuru, bagenzaga batyo.
