28:7 Bugufi bw'aho hantu hari igikingi cy'umutware w'icyo kirwa witwaga Pubiliyo, aratwakira atuzimanira neza iminsi itatu. 
28:8 Se wa Pubiliyo yari arwaye ubuganga n'amacinya. Nuko Pawulo yinjira mu nzu ye arasenga, amurambikaho ibiganza aramukiza. 
28:9 Ibyo bibaye, abandi barwayi bari mu kirwa baherako na bo baraza, arabakiza. 
28:10 Baduha icyubahiro cyinshi, kandi tugiye gutsuka bashyira ibyo twari dukennye byose mu nkuge yacu.
28:11 Tumazeyo amezi atatu dutsuka mu nkuge yavuye mu Alekizanderiya, yari imaze amezi y'imbeho ku kirwa, ikimenyetso cyayo cyari ishusho y'Abavandimwe b'Impanga. 
28:12 Dufata i Surakusa tumarayo iminsi itatu. 
28:13 Bukeye tuvayo, turagoronzoka tugera i Regiyo. Hashize umunsi umwe umuyaga uturutse ikusi urahuha, nuko tugenda iminsi ibiri dufata i Puteyoli. 
28:14 Tuhasanga bene Data bamwe, baratwinginga ngo tumarane na bo iminsi irindwi. Nuko tujya i Roma. 
28:15 Bene Data b'i Roma bumvise inkuru yacu, baza kudusanganirira mu midugudu yitwa Iguriro rya Apiyo, n'Amatundiro atatu. Pawulo ababonye ashima Imana, ashyitsa agatima mu nda.
28:16 Tumaze kugera i Roma, umutware utwara umutwe ashyikiriza imbohe umutware w'abasirikare barinda Kayisari, ariko bakundira Pawulo kuba ukwe, ari kumwe n'umusirikare umurinda.
28:17 Iminsi itatu ishize ahamagaza abakomeye bo mu Bayuda, bamaze guterana arababwira ati “Bagabo bene Data, nubwo ntagize ikibi nagiriye ubwoko bwacu cyangwa imigenzo ya ba sogokuruza, nabohewe i Yerusalemu, bankurayo bampa Abaroma. 
28:18 Na bo bamaze kumbaza bashaka kundekura, kuko nta mpamvu yambonetseho yo kunyicisha. 
28:19  Ariko Abayuda bagiye impaka, mpatwa kujuririra kuri Kayisari, icyakora si uko mfite icyo ndega ubwoko bwacu. 
28:20 Ni cyo nabatumiriye ngo tuvugane duhanganye, kuko ibyo Abisirayeli bīringira kuzabona, ari byo byatumye mboheshwa uyu munyururu.”
28:21 Na bo baramusubiza bati “Nta nzandiko z'ibyawe twabonye zivuye i Yudaya, kandi na bene Data baje nta wigeza atubarira inkuru mbi yawe, cyangwa ngo akuvuge nabi. 
28:22 Ariko turashaka kumva ibyo utekereza, kuko icyo gice tuzi yuko bakivuga nabi hose.”
28:23 Bamusezeranya umunsi, bamusanga ari benshi mu nzu bamucumbikiyemo arabibasobanurira, ahamya ubwami bw'Imana, abemeza ibya Yesu abikuye mu mategeko ya Mose no mu byahanuwe, ahera mu gitondo ageza nimugoroba. 
28:24 Bamwe bemera ibyo yavuze, ariko abandi ntibabyemera. 
28:25 Ntibahuza imitima, nuko Pawulo abasezeraho amaze kuvuga ijambo rimwe ati “Ibyo Umwuka Wera yabwiriye ba sekuruza wanyu mu kanwa k'umuhanuzi Yesaya, 
28:26   
28:27 Kuko umutima w'ubu bwoko ufite ibinure,
28:28 “Nuko mumenye yuko abanyamahanga bohererejwe ako gakiza k'Imana, kandi abo bazakumvira.”
28:29 Amaze kuvuga atyo, Abayuda bagenda bagishanya impaka cyane.]
